                <p class="text-cyan-600 font-medium mb-1">AIA Sri Lanka - IT Department</p>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-4">Jan 2025 - Feb 2026 | AIA Tower, Colombo 7</p>
                <ul class="text-slate-600 text-sm space-y-2 text-left list-disc list-inside">
                  <li>Engineered RESTful & GraphQL APIs in Software AG Designer using IBM DB2/SQL within ESB Linux systems.</li>
                  <li>Remediated security vulnerabilities via Veracode scans and automated file transfers with SFTP scripts.</li>
                  <li>Executed full SDLC using JAVA, Python, and PowerShell; managed deployments, Bitbucket, UAT, Azure, and OKTA CIAM.</li>
                  <li>Provided L2 Technical Support for SQL databases and real-time Workflow issues; managed Jira CRs and technical docs.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Education & Certifications Section -->
