              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-900">BSc (Hons) Software Engineering</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Cardiff Metropolitan University (ICBT Campus)</p>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-xs mt-1">Nov 2024 - Nov 2025 | Colombo 4</p>
                <div class="mt-4 border-t border-slate-200 pt-4">
