            <p class="text-cyan-600 text-xs font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider">BSc Final Year Project</p>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm mb-6 flex-grow">Developed a web-based platform recommending personalized life insurance products using an AI agent, AI chat bot and customer profiling.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-auto">
              <span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-semibold rounded-md group-hover:bg-cyan-50 transition-colors">Python (Flask)</span>
              <span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-semibold rounded-md group-hover:bg-cyan-50 transition-colors">React.js</span>
